The paper deals with image recognition and classification using convolutional neural networks (CNN) and neural attention mechanisms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses image captioning, which involves natural language processing, making cs.CL (Computation and Language) another likely category. The paper also deals with multimedia data, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves clustering and classification, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
